%html{:lang => "en"}
  %head
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}
    %meta{:content => "IE=edge", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}
    %meta{:content => "", :name => "description"}
    %meta{:content => "", :name => "author"}
    %title Faster Than Bastelfreak
    %link{:href => "//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.min.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
    %link{:href => "//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
    %link{:href => "/ftb/jumbotron-narrow.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}
  %body
    .container
      .header.clearfix
        %h3.text-muted
          %a{:href => "https://flipez.de/ftb"}
            faster than bastelfreak
            %span.label.label-danger Beta!
      .jumbotron
        %h1 be faster than bastelfreak
        %p.lead Find out how many times you are faster than bastel!
        %p
          %form{:method => "get"}
            .form-group
              %label{:for => "ftb-url"} Url
              %input#ftb-url.form-control{:type => "text", :name => "q", :value => url}
            %button.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{:type => "submit", :value => "Submit"} Compare
        %p
          =yield
        %hr
        %p
          %small
            Because bastelfreaks blog is so slow, each request will take up to 8 seconds. Please be patient.
            %br
            I will perform every request in realtime until bastelfreak is complaining about to much traffic.
        .container.text-muted
          %div.col-md-4
            %h1
              %span.fa.fa-question-circle
            bastelfreaks blog is loading slow, so lets find out how many times your website is faster
          %div.col-md-4
            %h1
              %span.fa.fa-cogs
            This little application is built with ruby and sinatra and deliverd by nginx
            %br
            %br
            No webservers are harmed during this test
          %div.col-md-4
            %h1
              %span.fa.fa-github
            You can help improving this application by contributing to the github repository
            %br
            %span.badge
              Coming soon!
        %hr
        %p
          %small.text-muted
            Discover how many awesomeness can fit in one blog by visiting
            %a{:href => "https://blog.bastelfreak.de/"} bastelfreaks blog
      %footer.footer
        %p 
          %a{:href => "/"} &copy; flipez.de 2015
